# API

Boxcar Developer Push Service API are used by developers to integrate Boxcar Service with developer back-end.

The [Publisher API](/api/publisher/) allows publishing notifications to developer user base, with a very fined-grained approach.
;T:preI"!
<h1 id="api">API</h1>

<p>Boxcar Developer Push Service API are used by developers to integrate Boxcar Service with developer back-end.</p>

<p>The <a href="/api/publisher/">Publisher API</a> allows publishing notifications to developer user base, with a very fined-grained approach.</p>
;T:	post@
I"/api/publisher/;T{;{	;I"Ìb<!DOCTYPE html>
