            <h2 class="title on-blog">Boxcar iOS SDK 1.0.14</h2>
            
        
            
<p>We released Boxcar iOS SDK 1.0.14 to remove any dependancy on Apple AdSupport.framework.
The new SDK is available in developer download area.</p>

            
