            <h2 class="title on-blog">Boxcar iOS SDK 1.0.15</h2>
            
        
            
<p>Boxcar Framework v.1.0.15 make the following changes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Support for XCode 5.1: Removed deprecation.</li>
  <li>Rename a few symbol that could conflict with AFNetworking.</li>
</ul>

<p>The new SDK is available in developer download area.</p>

            
