            <h2 class="title on-blog">Boxcar iOS SDK 1.0.16</h2>
            
        
            
<p>Boxcar Framework v.1.0.16 make the following changes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Support background task completion for running network operations.</li>
</ul>

<p>The new SDK is available in developer download area.</p>

            
