            <h2 class="title on-blog">Boxcar Android Demo 1.1.0.8</h2>
            
        
            
<p>Boxcar Demo v.1.1.0.8 makes the following changes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Uses new Boxcar API class</li>
  <li>Code clean up</li>
  <li>New demo project for Nokia X devices</li>
</ul>

<p>The new set of demos is available in developer download area.</p>

            
