            <h2 class="title on-blog">Boxcar Android Demo 1.1.0.11</h2>
            
        
            
<p>Boxcar Demo v.1.1.0.11 makes the following changes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Do use the new <em>start()</em> method, without passing the username; set username on each registration attempt</li>
  <li>Use MultipleUINotificationStrategy to show a single notification per push (do not group)</li>
  <li>Rename MainActivity to NormalNotificationActivity</li>
  <li>Set a custom default sound for pushes</li>
</ul>

<p>The new set of demos is available in developer download area.</p>

            
