            <h2 class="title on-blog">Boxcar iOS SDK 1.1.0 released with iOS 8 support</h2>
            
        
            
<p>Boxcar Framework v.1.1.0 has been released.</p>

<p>It is now compliant with iOS 8 (as well as previous iOS version from 6.1) and XCode 6.0. The new SDK fix the deprecation
and message log errors related to push notification approval on iOS 8.</p>

<!-- more -->

<p>We are in the process of releasing new iOS and Android feature in the coming weeks, including Action button support.
Please, get in touch with our development team if you would like to participate to the next SDK beta testing.</p>

<p>The new SDK is available in <a href="https://console.boxcar.io/downloads">Push Console Developer</a> download area.</p>

            
