Here is what you need to know about the upgrade operation.

<!-- more -->   

The change is related to [recent security issues found by Google](http://googleonlinesecurity.blogspot.co.uk/2014/10/this-poodle-bites-exploiting-ssl-30.html) relating to how browser negociate encryption protocol.
They found that there is some way to force browsers downgrading to less secure SSLv3 (under some special circumstances).
 
