            <h2 class="title on-blog">Boxcar Phonegap 1.0.3</h2>
            
        
            
<p>Boxcar Phonegap - Cordova SDK 1.0.3 has been released.</p>

<p>This is a minor improvement that grant easy access to the <em>extra</em> variables (metadata) you can pass in push notifications.</p>

<p>You can download that version from <a href="https://console.boxcar.io/downloads">Boxcar Developer Download Area</a>.</p>

            
