Boxcar Framework v.2.0.1 makes the following changes:

- Support for notification actions
- Fix problem losing previous state after app upgrade when version doesn't change
- Support for BigImage notifications
- Use ping only to track application activity
- Minor bugfixes

The new SDK is available in developer download area.
