    ga('create', 'UA-137362-14', 'boxcar.io');
    ga('send', 'pageview');
</script>
</body>
</html>
;T;	I"&
Boxcar Framework v.2.0.2 makes the following changes:

- Implement local tag subscription clean-up: On device registration, we now get the list of tags that are valid and list of tags that are deprecated. The SDK process the reply and only stores the tags that were reported as
valid. On the other hand, the registration event informs which tags were signaled as 'deprecated' and 'valid' by the server.
- PROGUARD processing: disable code optimization as this could case problems on ART devices

The new SDK is available in developer download area.
;T;
I"Y
<p>Boxcar Framework v.2.0.2 makes the following changes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Implement local tag subscription clean-up: On device registration, we now get the list of tags that are valid and list of tags that are deprecated. The SDK process the reply and only stores the tags that were reported as
valid. On the other hand, the registration event informs which tags were signaled as ‚Äòdeprecated‚Äô and ‚Äòvalid‚Äô by the server.</li>
  <li>PROGUARD processing: disable code optimization as this could case problems on ART devices</li>
</ul>

<p>The new SDK is available in developer download area.</p>
