  </li>
</ul>

<h2 class="title">
  <a href="/blog/2014-11-06-boxcar-android-sdk-1/">Boxcar Android SDK 1.1.0.13</a>
</h2>
    
<p>Boxcar Framework v.1.1.0.13 makes the following changes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Update and fix javadoc references</li>
  <li>Fix SecurityExceptions thrown by com.drippler.android.updates/.utils.openudid.OpenUDIDService on  Samsung Galaxy S4 devices.</li>
  <li>Support for notification actions</li>
  <li>Fix problem losing previous state after app upgrade when version doesn‚Äôt change</li>
  <li>Support for BigImage notifications</li>
  <li>Use ping only to track application activity</li>
  <li>Minor bugfixes</li>
</ul>

<p>The new SDK is available in developer download area.</p>

</div>

<p><br></p>
<hr>

<p><br></p>

