<ul>
  <li>Replaces BXCFacade class for Boxcar as the main SDK API</li>
  <li>Marks ping as failed if device is unregistered</li>
  <li>Updates Volley library version to 1.0-SNAPSHOT-04884d34</li>
</ul>

