<h1 id="client-creation-on-boxcar-push-console">Client creation on Boxcar Push Console</h1>

<h2 id="adding-an-ios-client-to-your-project">Adding an iOS client to your project</h2>

<p>With one or two certificates ready, as a Boxcar organisation owner, you can create your iOS application in the relevant project on Boxcar Push Console and upload one or two certificates.</p>

<ol>
  <li>Navigate to your project (Example: P1Framework).
<img src="/images/ios/push_console1_projects_list.png" alt="">
</li>
  <li>Select the client list.
<img src="/images/ios/push_console2_project.png" alt="">
</li>
  <li>Click on the button to add a client.
<img src="/images/ios/push_console3_project_client.png" alt="">
</li>
  <li>Enter client name and type (iOS).
<img src="/images/ios/push_console4_create_client.png" alt="">
</li>
  <li>Upload your certificates.
<img src="/images/ios/push_console5_client_upload_certificates.png" alt="">
</li>
</ol>


            
