    <title type="html">Boxcar Phonegap - Cordova Push plugin updated</title>
    <published>2014-11-05T23:00:00Z</published>
    <updated>2014-11-05T23:00:00Z</updated>
    <author>
      <name>mremond</name>
      <uri>https://github.com/mremond</uri>
    </author>
    <link rel="alternate" href="http://developer.boxcar.io/blog/2014-11-06-boxcar-phonegap-ios-8/">
    <content type="html">
&lt;p&gt;Boxcar Phonegap - Cordova Push plugin has been updated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is an update to support iOS 8 API changes for push notifications.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The SDK is also improved to support latest Boxcar API features, like sound notification handling and support for silent
notifications.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;!-- more --&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can upgrade your project to the latest version by issuing the following commands:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;cordova plugin rm net.process-one.boxcar-phonegap
cordova plugin rm com.phonegap.plugins.PushPlugin
cordova plugin add https://github.com/boxcar/boxcar-cordova-plugin
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
