<h1 id="android-sdk-documentation">Android SDK Documentation</h1>

<p>We recommend using the SDK 2.0.2 version, which supports the new GCM client from Google Play Library, and includes several enhancements that simplify the interaction with the framework.</p>

<p>Read <a href="2.0/">Android SDK 2.0.2 documentation</a>. </p>

<p>If you have already built your application based on the former SDK version and don‚Äôt want to perform changes to your code, then you can keep using it.</p>

<p>Read <a href="1.0/">Android SDK 1.1.0.14 documentation</a>.</p>

            
