<h1 id="nokia-x-sdk-introduction">Nokia X SDK Introduction</h1>

<p>Latest SDK Version: 1.1.0.7</p>

<ul id="markdown-toc">
  <li><a href="#nokia-notification-api-support">Nokia Notification API Support</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="nokia-notification-api-support">Nokia Notification API Support</h2>

<p>Our Android SDK supports standard Google Cloud Messaging, Amazon Device Messaging and Nokia Notification API.</p>

<p>With a single SDK you will be able to cover the tree Android flavors, making it simpler for developers to cover the major Android variants.</p>

<p>For details, please, refer to Boxcar <a href="/sdk/android/">Android SDK</a> documentation.</p>

            
